OL,3,CMinisters and MLAs urge restoration of
OL,4,Cfunding for city and growth deals
OL,6,FStormont ministers and MLAs from
OL,7,Facross the parties have united to
OL,8,Fdemand the restoration of funding for
OL,9,Ftwo city and growth deals in Northern
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,FFunding has been paused for the
OL,13,FCauseway Coast and Glens and Mid
OL,14,FSouthwest deals while the Labour
OL,15,FGovernment carries out a spending
OL,16,Freview after coming into office.
