OL,3,CMinisters and MLAs urge restoration of
OL,4,Cfunding for city and growth deals
OL,6,FInitially, the UK Government announced
OL,7,Fthe pausing of funding for four city
OL,8,Fand growth deals in the region, but it
OL,9,Flater emerged that deals covering
OL,10,FBelfast region and Londonderry City
OL,11,Fand Strabane will not be affected by
OL,12,Fthe suspension due to the advanced
OL,13,Fstage both were at.
OL,15,FThe whole of Northern Ireland is
OL,16,Fcovered by four city and growth deals
OL,17,Fworth a total of #1.7 billion with
OL,18,Fcontributions from Westminster,
OL,19,FStormont, local government and private
OL,20,Finvestment.
