OL,3,CMinisters and MLAs urge restoration of
OL,4,Cfunding for city and growth deals
OL,6,FThe Causeway Coast and Glens and Mid
OL,7,FSouthwest Growth Deals include the
OL,8,Ffunding of projects such as the
OL,9,Frestoration of the historic Armagh
OL,10,FGaol and the regeneration of Dungiven
OL,11,Fand Bushmills.
OL,13,FLeaders from the two deals met with
OL,14,FStormont Finance Minister Caoimhe
OL,15,FArchibald at Parliament Buildings on
OL,16,FMonday morning.
