OL,6,FThey later met with other ministers,
OL,7,Fincluding First Minister Michelle
OL,8,FO'Neill as well as MLAs who stood
OL,9,Ftogether for photographs in a show of
OL,10,Fsupport.
OL,12,FSpeaking in the chamber during
OL,13,Fquestions for the Executive Office, Ms
OL,14,FO'Neill said there was work to do in
OL,15,Fterms of fighting for the Mid
OL,16,FSouthwest and Causeway Coast and Glens
OL,17,Fdeals, which she said the Executive
OL,18,Fwas "determined to do".
