OL,3,CMinisters and MLAs urge restoration of
OL,4,Cfunding for city and growth deals
OL,6,FSpeaking to media, Ms Archibald said
OL,7,Fshe was unwavering in her commitment
OL,8,Fto the deals and called for the
OL,9,Fpausing of funding from Westminster to
OL,10,Fbe "lifted immediately".
OL,12,F"The continuation is undermining
OL,13,Fconfidence and momentum in the
OL,14,Fdelivery of these deals, a point that
OL,15,Fwas made to me by the deal partners
OL,16,Fthis morning, and today has once again
OL,17,Freinforced that there is unanimous
OL,18,Fpolitical support for this pause to be
OL,19,Flifted," she said.
