OL,3,CMinisters and MLAs urge restoration of
OL,4,Cfunding for city and growth deals
OL,6,F"My focus is on making the case for
OL,7,Fthese deals and working with the deal
OL,8,Fpartners to ensure their case is
OL,9,Fcommunicated very clearly to the
OL,10,FBritish Government, that this funding
OL,11,Fhas been committed and they need to
OL,12,Fhonour their commitments to delivering
OL,13,Fon the funding to these deals,
OL,14,Fprojects that have been worked on for
OL,15,Fa number of years.
OL,17,F"A great deal of time, effort and
OL,18,Fcommitment has went in to the
OL,19,Fdevelopment of these projects and they
OL,20,Fwill be game-changing.
