OL,3,CMinisters and MLAs urge restoration of
OL,4,Cfunding for city and growth deals
OL,6,F"I have had the opportunity to go out
OL,7,Fand to visit each of the deal areas,
OL,8,Fand to get a sense of what the
OL,9,Fprojects mean to the communities on
OL,10,Fthe ground, so they now need to have
OL,11,Fthe reassurance that they can get on
OL,12,Fahead and deliver these deals so we
OL,13,Fcan see the benefits to our local
OL,14,Fcommunities."
OL,16,FDavid Jackson, chief executive of
OL,17,FCauseway Coast and Glens Borough
OL,18,FCouncil, said the pausing of the
OL,19,Ffunding had been a "real body blow"
OL,20,Ffor the local economy.
