OL,3,CMinisters and MLAs urge restoration of
OL,4,Cfunding for city and growth deals
OL,6,F"We've been working on this deal for
OL,7,Fseveral years, we're trying to focus
OL,8,Fon the positives and hope this deal
OL,9,Fstill proceeds because it is
OL,10,Fpotentially a game-changer," he said.
OL,12,F"I can tell you at the moment we have
OL,13,Fprivate investment waiting to roll
OL,14,Finto the area and they won't sit
OL,15,Faround for too long. We've got some
OL,16,Ffabulous projects that have already
OL,17,Fbeen through business cases. They're
OL,18,Fvery robust and a real opportunity to
OL,19,Fprovide high-value jobs and further
OL,20,Finvestment.
