OL,3,CMinisters and MLAs urge restoration of
OL,4,Cfunding for city and growth deals
OL,6,F"I have complete confidence in the
OL,7,FExecutive. This morning, they were
OL,8,Fstanding shoulder to shoulder with us,
OL,9,Fputting pressure on the British
OL,10,FGovernment."
OL,12,FCouncillor Kevin Savage, chair of the
OL,13,FMid Southwest governance group, said
OL,14,Fthey are hopeful their deal will go
OL,15,Fahead.
OL,17,F"It's too big to fail at this stage,
OL,18,Ffive years have gone into this project
OL,19,Fso far," he said.
